FAKHOURY
v.
FAKHOURY. No. 441P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2005. Victoria Bender, Raleigh, for Kimberly Fakhoury.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th day of September 2005 by Defendant to Withdraw Petition:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of October 2005."
